caption:
So, you want to get a puppy? We don't blame you, look at those eyes! 

Our partners at @bosleys.place happen to have some pups who are looking for their forever home! If you're in the Atlanta area, consider adopting one of these lil' fellas. You'll get a new best friend for life and a free first box of food plus a $350 credit to The Farmer's Dog.

Check out our link in bio for terms and conditions.
